{"root":{"data":{"id":"djuxdv6yaj40","created":1783690142272,"text":"使用部件亲和场的实时多人二维姿态估计"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djuxfb0391c0","created":1783690255050,"text":"摘要"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djuxg1tr1gg0","created":1783690313440,"text":"研究背景"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djuxga9hzvs0","created":1783690331806,"text":"高效检测图像中多个人的2D姿态是一个挑战，尤其是在人数未知、存在接触和遮挡的情况下，运行复杂度会随之增加"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djuxg3o1en40","created":1783690317448,"text":"研究发现"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djuxho4byso0","created":1783690440333,"text":"出了一种名为Part Affinity Fields (PAFs)的非参数表示方法"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djuxhvdz6140","created":1783690456153,"text":"通过学习将身体部位与个体关联起来，并采用贪婪的 bottom-up 解析步骤，实现了实时性能和高精度"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djuxi1eerww0","created":1783690469240,"text":"研究方向"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djuxi3oy2io0","created":1783690474231,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]}]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}